Reverso, the birth of the first icon.
#ReversoStories
_
The first Reverso, 1931.
Patrimony Jaeger-LeCoultre.
_
Elegant, pure, and refined, the Reverso was invented in 1931 for British army officers in India who were willing to protect the crystal of their watches while playing polo. Representing perfect balance between sport, innovation and refined elegance, Reverso has since become a watchmaking icon. 
_
